This line might be the problem:
var a = btoa(s.toString())

"s" here is actually a Buffer with encoded data. When you do .toString(),
you lose the encoding.

Instead, I recommend either of these:
var a = s.toString("base64");
Or
var a = iconv.decode(s, "base64");

Also please make sure to read these wiki pages for more context:
